OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1777471867
OL,3,CChelsea captain Millie Bright
OL,4,Cannounces retirement from football
OL,6,FChelsea captain Millie Bright has
OL,7,Fannounced her retirement from football.
OL,9,FThe 32-year-old defender from
OL,10,FChesterfield holds Chelsea's all-time
OL,11,Fappearance record (314) and has won
OL,12,Fsix Women's FA Cup trophies.
OL,14,FThe decision comes after Millie Bright
OL,15,Fannounced her retirement from
OL,16,Finternational football last year.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
