CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1777471867
OL,3,CChelsea captain Millie Bright
OL,4,Cannounces retirement from football
OL,6,FIn a statement Bright said:
OL,7,F"Representing Chelsea over the last 12
OL,8,Fyears has been everything to me, but
OL,9,FI'm now ready to say goodbye to
OL,10,Fplaying football. I've given all I
OL,11,Fcan, and I never wanted to fight for
OL,12,Fany other badge.
OL,14,F"It is now time, and I'm ready to go
OL,15,Finto a new era. I'm always going to be
OL,16,FChelsea, but just in a different way."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
