PN,40403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1777471867
OL,3,CChelsea captain Millie Bright
OL,4,Cannounces retirement from football
OL,6,FUpon announcing her retirement,
OL,7,FChelsea said she will be staying on as
OL,8,Fa trustee of the club's foundation and
OL,9,Fwill take up a new role as club
OL,10,Fambassador.
OL,12,FOver her 12-year career at Chelsea
OL,13,FMillie Bright has collected 20
OL,14,Ftrophies.
OL,16,FChelsea say: "She ends her career as a
OL,17,Ftrue Chelsea legend and our longest-
OL,18,Fserving player, having been part of
OL,19,Fthe club's first trophy win in 2015
OL,20,Fand the 19 that have followed since.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
