PN,40404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1777471867
OL,3,CChelsea captain Millie Bright
OL,4,Cannounces retirement from football
OL,6,F"Everyone at Chelsea is so proud of
OL,7,FMillie's contribution to the club and
OL,8,Fthe women's game during its
OL,9,Funprecedented period of growth.
OL,11,F"We look forward to continuing to work
OL,12,Fwith her as she moves into her roles
OL,13,Foff the pitch with the club."
OL,15,FBorn in Derbyshire, she began her
OL,16,Fcareer as a youngster with Sheffield
OL,17,FUnited before moving across South
OL,18,FYorkshire to Doncaster Rovers Belles.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
