PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1777471867
OL,3,CChelsea captain Millie Bright
OL,4,Cannounces retirement from football
OL,6,FShe began her Chelsea career in the
OL,7,F2015 season and went on to play more
OL,8,FWomen's Super League matches than any
OL,9,Fother player.
OL,11,FIn Chelsea's 2024/25 unbeaten domestic
OL,12,Fseason, Millie Bright made 36
OL,13,Fappearances, as captain of the club.
OL,15,FChelsea confirmed a tribute will be
OL,16,Fpaid to Bright during their final WSL
OL,17,Fmatch of this season against
OL,18,FManchester United on May 16 at
OL,19,FStamford Bridge.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
