PN,40406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1777471867
OL,3,CChelsea captain Millie Bright
OL,4,Cannounces retirement from football
OL,6,FBright's retirement from football
OL,7,Fcomes after she called time on her
OL,8,Finternational career in October 2025,
OL,9,Fhaving won the European Championship
OL,10,Fon home soil before skippering the
OL,11,FLionesses to the World Cup final the
OL,12,Ffollowing year.
OL,14,FBright made her debut for England in
OL,15,FSeptember 2016, before going on to
OL,16,Fearn 88 caps and score six goals for
OL,17,Fher country.
OL,19,FShe also represented Team GB at the
OL,20,FTokyo Olympics in 2021.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
