PN,40407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1777471867
OL,3,CChelsea captain Millie Bright
OL,4,Cannounces retirement from football
OL,6,FIn 2024 Bright was recognised with an
OL,7,FOBE in the King's New Year's Honours
OL,8,FList of 2024, acknowledging her
OL,9,Fleadership and impact on the game.
OL,11,FLionesses head coach Sarina Wiegman
OL,12,Fpaid tribute to Bright, and added:
OL,13,F"Millie has played such a big role in
OL,14,Fthe growth of the women's game, with
OL,15,Fboth England and Chelsea, and she has
OL,16,Fachieved so much along the way. What
OL,17,Fshe has given to her club and country
OL,18,Fis incredible.
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
