FL,405,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F404A1777471867
OL,3,CChelsea captain Millie Bright
OL,4,Cannounces retirement from football
OL,6,F"It is hard to put into words the
OL,7,Fimpact she has had. She has inspired
OL,8,Fso many people, pushed standards and
OL,9,Fshown girls and boys what can be
OL,10,Fachieved in the sport.
OL,12,F"Winning EURO 2022 and captaining
OL,13,FEngland to the World Cup Final in
OL,14,FAustralia says so much about her, but
OL,15,Fit is not just about the trophies with
OL,16,Fclub and country. She has also earned
OL,17,Fgreat respect through the way she has
OL,18,Fcommitted herself to the game."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
